rows.label: qst200404_msg0001
rows.name:
The loan shark? Nah man, I
wouldn't borrow money from
him even if you paid me.

rows.label: qst200404_msg0002
rows.name:
Why? For one, I hear he's in
cahoots with that quack Celian.

rows.label: qst200404_msg0003
rows.name:
I understand medical fees, but charging
an arm and two legs, sending people to a
moneylender if they can't afford it...?

rows.label: qst200404_msg0004
rows.name:
That's some evil scary
stuff right there.

rows.label: qst200404_msg0005
rows.name:
If you need a doctor,
whatever you do, make sure
you don't go to Celian!

rows.label: qst200404_msg0101
rows.name: Watch out for that quack Celian!
